<section class="laf" id="life-after-fba">
  <div class="laf-inner">

    <div class="laf-header reveal">
      <h2 class="display-headline laf-headline">
        What Your Life Is Going to Look Like<br /><em>After FBA.</em>
      </h2>
    </div>

    <div class="laf-body">
      <p class="body-lora laf-para reveal">
        Now I want to make it perfectly clear. I'm not promising you a life of wealth and complete
        freedom like I'm offering you a cookie. It takes commitment, it takes consistent action and hard work.
      </p>

      <p class="body-lora laf-para reveal">
        Sure FBA bought me back my time and gave me the life of financial freedom that I long craved,
        but it didn't happen overnight, it took trials and hardship.
      </p>

      <p class="body-lora laf-para reveal">
        But with the right mentor and a well built system, I can promise a chance to build
        something great for yourself so you can have a shot at living your freedom and spending
        more time with your loved ones.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Testimonials placeholder -->

  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .laf {
    background: #1A1A1A;
    padding: 130px 0 110px;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .laf::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    height: 1px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, transparent, var(--color-gold), transparent);
    opacity: 0.2;
  }

  .laf-inner {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 60px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .laf-header {
    margin-bottom: 64px;
  }

  .laf-headline {
    font-size: clamp(30px, 4vw, 56px);
    color: #fff;
    line-height: 1.1;
  }

  .laf-headline em {
    color: var(--color-gold);
    font-style: italic;
  }

  .laf-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  .laf-para {
    color: #fff;
    font-size: 18px;
    opacity: 0.65;
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

@media (max-width: 700px) {
    .laf { padding: 72px 0 64px; }
    .laf-inner { padding: 0 24px; }
    .laf-header { margin-bottom: 48px; }
  }
</style>
